Package com.redis.foundation.data

Class DataItemAnalyzer

java.lang.Object
com.redis.foundation.data.DataItemAnalyzer
public class DataItemAnalyzer extends Object
The Data Item Analyzer class will examine small-to-medium sized data sets to determine their type and value composition. A good enhancement to this package would be the inclusion of the Apache Commons Math features - see link below.
Since:
1.0
Author:
Al Cole

    • getDetails

      public DataDoc getDetails(int aSampleCount)
      Returns a DataDoc of items describing the scanned value data. The DataDoc will contain the item name, derived type, populated count, null count and a sample count of values (with overall percentages) that repeated most often.
      Parameters:
      aSampleCount - Identifies the top count of values.
      Returns:
      DataDoc instance of analysis details.
